## RelationType: 方案使用备份窗口

通过 `backup_solution.id` 匹配 `backup_window.backup_solution_id`，将备份方案关联到其下属的多个备份窗口条目。

### Endpoint

| Source | Target | Type |
|--------|--------|------|
| backup_solution | backup_window | direct |

### Mapping Rules

| Source Property | Target Property |
|-----------------|------------------|
| id | backup_solution_id |
